Oh, thank you. I am new here. I thought #implementaters would be appropriate. Thanks.

#implementers is the correct default place to ask anything. However, it's a really busy stream, so some people choose to only monitor more specific streams. Posting to #javascript will catch the attention of fewer people overall, but should catch the attention of more people interested in JavaScript :)
